These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-6-1::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skiing, skateboarding, rowing
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, car, bus
3 different games are played: scrabble, go, bridge
House: modern, craftsman, wooden
City: london, miami, berlin
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, chinese, spanish
 1. the person playing bridge is in an odd position##4
 2. the person who's sport is skiing is in the middle##1
 3. the spanish is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
 4. the person driving the bus is on the left or right of the person traveling to miami##3
 5. the modern house is not the person who's sport is skateboarding##6
 6. the person driving the car is on the far right##1
 7. the craftsman house is in an even position##4
 8. the person who's sport is skateboarding is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to berlin##5
 9. the person playing go is between the person traveling to london and the spanish##2
10. the chinese is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |      3      |
| Beverage      | rowing        | skiing        | skateboarding    |
| Hobby         | roller    | bus       | car      |
| Job           | bridge | go | scrabble |
| Movie-Genre   | modern     | craftsman   | wooden |
| Music-Genre   | london       | berlin      | miami      |
| Nationality   | canadian   | chinese      | spanish     |

