.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-6-17::.
3 different games are played: bridge, chess, snooker
City: boston, edinburgh, rome
3 different pets are kept: turtle, pony, rat
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: crime, drama, time-travel
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: electronic, indie, trance
The people have 3 different hobbies: sudoku, baking, collecting
 1. the owner of the pony is in an even position##4
 2. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far right##1
 3. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to rome##5
 4. the person watching crime movies is the person who's hobby is baking##1
 5. the person traveling to rome is on the far left##1
 6. the person playing snooker is not the fan trance##6
 7. the person playing chess is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
 8. the fan indie is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
 9. the person playing snooker is on the left or right of the fan electronic##3
10. the fan trance is on the left or right of the person traveling to edinburgh##3
11. the fan trance is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |       2        |      3      |
